item.title: CVE-2020-7818|2024-09-17T03:23:12.174Z -- humantolk%20co.ltd -- daviewindy
item.description: DaviewIndy 8.98.9 and earlier has a Heap-based overflow vulnerability, triggered when the user opens a malformed PDF file that is mishandled by Daview.exe. Attackers could exploit this and arbitrary code execution.
